Description: Suntuitive Glass is dynamic glass that is driven by the environment.
Full Description: suntuitive uses heat from direct sunlight to tint when necessary.  As the sun moves across the sky, Suntuitive Glass will cool and return to clear. At night or in cloudy conditions, when direct sun is not present, Suntuitive Glass remains clear and allows as much daylighting as possible. Suntuitive Glass is the most advanced, yet simplest, dynamic glass technology available. With Suntuitive Glass, architects, building owners, building professionals and home owners can specify an adaptive glazing system that transitions seamlessly between clear and tinted.
